name: Jaidenanimations
description:
I was curious to see how a waifu-generating model would handle a relatively simple character. I'm pretty happy with the results, but don't tell Twitter about this one.

With the right prompt, anything above 1 will match her hairstyle and colors, but I recommend 1.1-1.5 if you want to capture her flat cartoon-y style.

Support me on Ko-Fi!

modelVersions.description: Trained on NAI, tested models listed in sample images.
